NK037(ji)013:1: // stag zhon gyi sgrub thabs dbang chog dang bcas pa bzhugs /
NK037(ji)013:3: sangs rgyas kun gyi mthu stobs gzugs //
NK037(ji)013:4: drag po'i gar gyis rnam rol pa //
NK037(ji)013:5: stag zhon mgon la gus btud nas //
NK037(ji)013:6: gang de'i sgrub thabs nyung ngur bri //
NK037(ji)013:7: 'dir dpal mgon stag zhon gnubs lugs kyi sgrubs thabs dang 'brel bar dbang bskur ba la gsum ste /
NK037(ji)013:8: sbyor ba yo byad kyi shoms /
NK037(ji)013:9: dngos gzhi sgrub pa'i thabs dang /
NK037(ji)013:11: dang po yo byad bsham pa ni /
NK037(ji)013:12: gnas dpen par nyer dgu sogs dus khyad par can la /
NK037(ji)013:13: bris sku la sogs pa'i rten bshams pa'i mdud du /
NK037(ji)013:14: man+dala gru gsum mthing nag la lha grangs kyi tshom bu bkod /
NK037(ji)013:15: de'i dbus su gtor ma sku rten dang mda' dar nag pos brgyan pa bzhag /
NK037(ji)013:16: mtha' mchod gtor sogs dam rdzas rnams kyis bskor /
NK037(ji)013:17: nyer mkho'i yo byad thams cad tshogs par bsham mo //
NK037(ji)013:19: bdag bskyed gsang ba'i bdag po'am /
NK037(ji)013:20: yi dam khro bo gang rung gi rnal 'byor la gnas pas /
NK037(ji)013:21: spyi dang khyad par gyi mchod pa rnams byin gyis brlabs /
NK037(ji)013:23: stong pa'i ngang las dur khrod chen po'i sa gzhir
NK037(ji)013:24: e las byung ba'i chos 'byung mthing nag 'bar ba'i
NK037(ji)013:25: nang du pad nyi la gnas pa'i h+aum mthing nag
NK037(ji)013:27: dgra bgegs thams cad tshar bcad /
NK037(ji)013:28: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las dpal ye shes
NK037(ji)013:29: kyi mgon po stag zhon nag po sku mdog dus
NK037(ji)013:31: zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK037(ji)013:32: spyan gsum sdang mig g.yo zhing dbu skra dang sma ra smin ma 'bar ba /
NK037(ji)013:33: phyag g.yas tsan+dana gyi beng chen nam mkhar 'phyar zhing /
NK037(ji)013:34: g.yon lcags par khrag gis gang ba zhal du gsol ba /
NK037(ji)013:35: dar nag gi ber chen dgu brtsegs gsol zhing gser gyi ske rags bcings pa /
NK037(ji)013:40: gser gyi rna cha la sogs pas brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)013:41: chibs su stag chen rngam pa chibs shing /
NK037(ji)013:42: seng ge rol du khrid pa /
NK037(ji)013:43: lcags kyi bya khra klad la lding zhing /
NK037(ji)013:44: lce spyang dom dred phyi nas 'brang ba /
NK037(ji)013:45: me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK037(ji)013:46: g.yon du b+h+yo las lha mo dmar nag khram shing dang nad rkyal 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)013:47: lcags kyi drel rta rkang gsum la chibs shing rlung nag 'tshubs ma'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK037(ji)013:48: yab yum de dag gi g.yas su sku'i mon pa
NK037(ji)013:49: srog bdag sngo skya tri sh+au la'i rtse la mi
NK037(ji)013:50: ro btsugs pa'i rgyal mtshan 'phyar ba /
NK037(ji)013:51: g.yon du gsung gi mon pa bshan pa dmar nag g.yas ma he'i rwa dung 'bud cing /
NK037(ji)013:52: g.yon phur bu dang zhags pas dam nyams 'ching ba /
NK037(ji)013:53: mdun du thugs kyi mon pa the'u nag po spu gri dang mi snying thogs pa /
NK037(ji)013:54: gzhan yang sha zan gyi mon pa /
NK037(ji)013:60: tshe 'phrog gi mon pa rnams las mkhan gyi cha lugs can /
NK037(ji)013:61: g.yas ral gri sogs mtshon cha sna tshogs dang /
NK037(ji)013:63: de'i phyi rol du ma mo bdun la sogs pa
NK037(ji)013:64: ma mo mkha' 'gro sha za grangs med pa dang
NK037(ji)013:73: rdo rje gdan la sogs pa nas mgon po 'khor
NK037(ji)013:74: bcas badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs par bsam la
NK037(ji)013:76: dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa //
NK037(ji)013:77: lcang lo can gyi pho brang nas //
NK037(ji)013:78: lha chen ma h+aa k+aa la dang //
NK037(ji)013:79: lcam mo dpal ldan re ma t+ai //
NK037(ji)013:80: 'khor dang bcas pa ma lus pa //
NK037(ji)013:81: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba dang //
NK037(ji)013:82: dam nyams dgra bo bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)013:84: ma h+aa k+aa la tri yam dza dzah trag rak+sha
NK037(ji)013:85: sa ma ya man+da la a kad+d+h+ya a be sha
NK037(ji)013:86: ya a be sha ya tish+tha tish+tha a ba lo
NK037(ji)013:87: ka ya h+aum h+aum h+aum dzah zhes spyan drangs /
NK037(ji)013:89: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i spyan snga ru //
NK037(ji)013:90: khas blangs dam bcas ma g.yel bar //
NK037(ji)013:92: bzhugs la bcol ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK037(ji)013:93: dzahh+aum bam hohm h+aa k+aa la tish+tha badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK037(ji)013:94: zhes dam tshig pa dang dbyer med du bzhugs su gsol /
NK037(ji)013:96: badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa la sa pa ri w+aa ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK037(ji)013:97: zhes dam la bzhag rdo rje rtse lnga pas dbu brgyan par bsam mo //
NK037(ji)013:99: lha min dmag tshogs g.yul bzlog cing //
NK037(ji)013:100: lha dmag dkar po'i dbugs 'byin pa //
NK037(ji)013:101: legs ldan nag po 'khor bcas la //
NK037(ji)013:102: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK037(ji)013:103: a ti p+au hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh zhes phyag bya /
NK037(ji)013:106: gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs rnams kyi //
NK037(ji)013:107: dmar gyi ar+g+ham dbang po lnga //
NK037(ji)013:108: gsur chen spos dang zhun chen me //
NK037(ji)013:109: sbyar ba'i dri dang zhal zas mchog /
NK037(ji)013:110: snyan brjid rol mo'i mchod pa dang //
NK037(ji)013:111: sha lnga dang ni bdud rtsi lnga //
NK037(ji)013:112: nya sha la du la phug dang //
NK037(ji)013:113: 'bru bcud chang dang khur ba dang //
NK037(ji)013:115: ba lim bdud rtsi'i gtor ma sogs //
NK037(ji)013:116: phyi nang gsang ba'i dam tshig rdzas //
NK037(ji)013:117: longs spyod lnga ldan 'di dag kun //
NK037(ji)013:119: thugs dam dbang gis bzhes su gsol //
NK037(ji)013:120: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham nas shap+da'i bar dang /
NK037(ji)013:122: tshig rigs mthun sngags dang bcas pas 'bul ba'am /
NK037(ji)013:123: bsdu na gong gi sngags mthar /
NK037(ji)013:124: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta p+au dza kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)013:127: khyad par du ljags byin gyis brlabs te /
NK037(ji)013:129: ba lim i dam gri h+na kha kha kh+aa hi
NK037(ji)013:130: kh+aa hi b+huny+dza hoh rak+ta pi pa to sa ma
NK037(ji)013:131: ya s+w+aa h+aa / zhes pa bdun gyis phul la /
NK037(ji)013:132: dpal ma h+aa k+aa la khrag 'thung gi rgyal po sogs nas /
NK037(ji)013:133: bstan pa'i bka' srung chen po legs ldan stag zhon
NK037(ji)013:134: nag po 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyis mchod sbyin
NK037(ji)013:135: gyi gtor ma rgya chen po 'di bzhes la sogs
NK037(ji)013:136: phrin las gsol / bstod pa ni /
NK037(ji)013:138: bde chen 'du 'bral med pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK037(ji)013:139: yang dag rngam pa'i sku gcig byung ba ni //
NK037(ji)013:140: mthing nag mi bsrun 'jigs byed 'bar ba'i sku //
NK037(ji)013:141: legs ldan dpa' bo che btsan drag shul can //
NK037(ji)013:142: sa gsum dbang bsgyur nag po che la bstod //
NK037(ji)013:143: bstan dgra 'joms mdzad khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)013:144: khrag mtshor rgyug cing khams gsum skad cig nyul //
NK037(ji)013:145: ma cig re ma t+ai la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)013:146: legs ldan nag po'i sku gsung thugs las sprul //
NK037(ji)013:147: dgra bgegs sgrol mdzad dregs pa bdun du bstan //
NK037(ji)013:148: phrin las pho nya dur khrod ma mo bdun //
NK037(ji)013:149: ye shes dbyings kyis sprul pa'i 'khor la bstod //
NK037(ji)013:150: rnam 'phrul pho nya ma nges sna tshogs pa //
NK037(ji)013:151: mche ba can dang bya gcan gdugs pa'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)013:152: sde brgyad 'khor dang bcas la bstod pa 'bul //
NK037(ji)013:153: bdag cag re smon dus 'dir 'grub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)013:156: mgon po 'khor bcas kyi thugs kar nyi ma la
NK037(ji)013:157: gnas pa'i h+aum yig gi mthar so so'i sngags kyi
NK037(ji)013:158: bskor ba bdag gi thugs ka'i 'od kyis bskul bas
NK037(ji)013:159: ci 'dod pa'i phrin las rab 'byams thogs med du
NK037(ji)013:161: ma h+aa k+aa la r+au pa h+aum phata /
NK037(ji)013:163: ma h+aa k+aa la rak+sha du beng ni dzah gsung gi snying po'o //
NK037(ji)013:164: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la tri yam dza dzahdagra bo m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK037(ji)013:165: thugs kyi snying po ste bzlas pa' gtso bo 'di la byed /
NK037(ji)013:166: trag rak+sha ha la dgra bo m+aa ra ya dza dzah lha mo'i snying po'o //
NK037(ji)013:167: du na ru dra thum b+ha ti dzah sh+au la
NK037(ji)013:168: ra tsa tri sham dzah badz+ra tri sna sa d+hu
NK037(ji)013:169: kha thum tri sa ma ya dza dgra bo m+aa
NK037(ji)013:171: ces mon pa'i sngags te gtso 'khor gyi 'gros sbyar
NK037(ji)013:172: nas ci rigs bzlas pa'i mthar mchod cing phrin las
NK037(ji)013:173: gsol / tshogs mchod dang bskang bshags sogs spro na skabs 'dir bya /
NK037(ji)013:174: rgyun du thun gtor yod na /
NK037(ji)013:176: lha yi sde dpon tshogs kyi bdag /
NK037(ji)013:177: dpal ldan ma h+aa k+aa la ni //
NK037(ji)013:178: lha mo gnyan dang gnyis su med //
NK037(ji)013:180: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK037(ji)013:181: zhes sogs spyi dang mthun par stob /
NK037(ji)013:186: smon lam shis brjod rnams bya'o //
NK037(ji)013:187: bsnyen sgrub las gsum gyi gdams pa rnams yig rnying
NK037(ji)013:188: las shes shing 'dir ni gtor chog tsam smos pa'o
NK037(ji)013:189: // gsum pa dbang gi cho ga ni /
NK037(ji)013:190: bdag mdun gyi sgrub mchod bzlas pa'i bar dang phrin las gsol ba rnams sngar bzhin bya'o //
NK037(ji)013:191: slob ma'i bya ba khrus dang phyag byas /
NK037(ji)013:192: bgegs skrod pa rnams sngon du 'gro bas /
NK037(ji)013:193: mtshams sbyor ci rigs pa bshad nas /
NK037(ji)013:194: khyad par 'dir dpal ye shes kyi mgon po stag
NK037(ji)013:195: zhon nag po zhes bya ba bstan pa'i bka' srung
NK037(ji)013:196: thams cad kyi che btsan mthu stobs dang nus pa'i
NK037(ji)013:197: byin rlabs gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa de
NK037(ji)013:198: yin / de yang rdo rje 'chang chen pos 'di'i
NK037(ji)013:199: rgyud gsungs te gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo
NK037(ji)013:200: yin / rje la gtad / de nas slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas dang //
NK037(ji)013:202: ba su d+ha ra sogs rig 'dzin grub thob rnams las brgyud de /
NK037(ji)013:203: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes la bka' babs pa nyid /
NK037(ji)013:204: dge bshes grwa pa kun grags nas /
NK037(ji)013:207: lce mdo sde seng ge sogs las brgyud pa'i skor dang /
NK037(ji)013:208: shin tu zab pa bka' rgya can rnams gnubs kyis
NK037(ji)013:209: skor tsho gsum du phyes nas gter du sbas pa
NK037(ji)013:210: ste / nor srung ltar sgrub pa beng ma'i skor rnams nyug gi rdo rje sgrom bu dang /
NK037(ji)013:211: bka' sdod ltar sgrub pa tri yam ma'i skor phung po ri bo che dang /
NK037(ji)013:212: drag sngags su sgrub pa dug gi spu gri'i skor
NK037(ji)013:213: g.yung gi rdza lhung mor gter du sbas pa rnams
NK037(ji)013:214: / rgya zhang khrom rdo rje 'bar gyis gter nas bton pa rog grags seng /
NK037(ji)013:216: lce mdo sde seng ge sogs las brgyud pa ste /
NK037(ji)013:217: bka' gter brgyud pa gnyis ldan gyi rjes gnang zab mo sgrub par byed pa la /
NK037(ji)013:218: slob dpon gyi bya ba rnams sngon du song /
NK037(ji)013:219: slob ma'i bya ma la sngon 'gro dang dngos gzhi gnyis las /
NK037(ji)013:221: gsol ba 'debs pa thugs rje chen po mnga' ba'i bdag /
NK037(ji)013:222: slob dpon khyod ni dgongs su gsol //
NK037(ji)013:223: bstan pa'i dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)013:224: mgon bo'i sgrub thabs bdag la stsol //
NK037(ji)013:227: dpal mgon ma h+aa k+aa la 'di //
NK037(ji)013:228: khyod kyis legs par mchod nus sam //
NK037(ji)013:229: phrin las bcol dang dam tshig rnams //
NK037(ji)013:230: rjes su mthun par byed nus sam //
NK037(ji)013:232: des kyang nus par khas blangs /
NK037(ji)013:234: snod dang ldan pa'i bu khyod kyis //
NK037(ji)013:235: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)013:236: mgon po'i sgrub pa ngas byin gyis //
NK037(ji)013:237: khyod kyis spro bas brtson par mchod //
NK037(ji)013:239: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK037(ji)013:242: slob dpon gyis slob ma nyid bdag bskyed kyi yi dam du sgom tshul phog nas /
NK037(ji)013:243: mdun du dur khrod chen po'i sa gzhir e las byung ba'i chos 'byung mthing nag sogs nas /
NK037(ji)013:244: grangs med pa dang bcas pas bskor ba'o //
NK037(ji)013:245: zhes pa'i bar gong bzhin mdun bskyed gsal 'debs su gzhug /
NK037(ji)013:246: slob dpon la mos gus dung byas pas slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK037(ji)013:247: mdun bskyed mgon po'i thugs kar phog pas thugs brgyud bskul /
NK037(ji)013:248: mgon po'i thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK037(ji)013:249: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs ka nas mgon po'i
NK037(ji)013:250: sku che chung bsam gyis mi khyab pa spyan drangs
NK037(ji)013:251: lus la thim par mos shig /
NK037(ji)013:252: ces brjod la sngags dang rol mo'i sgra sbyar /
NK037(ji)013:253: sku rten spyi bor bzhag la /
NK037(ji)013:255: dam tshig can gyi bu khyod la //
NK037(ji)013:256: dpal mgon sku yi dbang bskur bas //
NK037(ji)013:257: khyod kyi rgyun du sgrub pa dang //
NK037(ji)013:258: sku yi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK037(ji)013:262: yang slob dpon la mos gus byas pas /
NK037(ji)013:263: slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis /
NK037(ji)013:264: mdun bskyed dang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs ka nas sngags kyi yi ge dpag med spyan drangs /
NK037(ji)013:265: khyed rang gi mgrin par thim par mos shig byas la /
NK037(ji)013:268: dpal chen gsung gi dbang bskur bas //
NK037(ji)013:269: bsnyen sgrub sngags rnams bzlas pa yis //
NK037(ji)013:270: ngag gi nus pa mthar phyin nas //
NK037(ji)013:271: gsung gi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK037(ji)013:273: w+aa ka a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah zhes dang /
NK037(ji)013:274: slob dpon dang mdun bskyed kyi thugs ka nas sngags
NK037(ji)013:275: kyi phreng ba thon pa slob ma'i khar zhugs snying
NK037(ji)013:276: ga'i sa bon gyi mthar 'khod par bsam la sngags
NK037(ji)013:277: kyi rjes zlos lan gsum byed du gzhug /
NK037(ji)013:279: yang slob dpon la mos gus byas pas /
NK037(ji)013:280: slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis mdun bskyed
NK037(ji)013:281: dang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs ka nas phyag
NK037(ji)013:283: khyed rang gi snying gar thim par mos shig byas la /
NK037(ji)013:284: tsan+dana gyi bing lag g.yas su gtad de /
NK037(ji)013:286: ma h+aa k+aa la'i phyag mtshan ni //
NK037(ji)013:287: tsan+dana beng chen sgo gsum pa //
NK037(ji)013:288: lha dang lha min dmag tshogs 'gyed //
NK037(ji)013:289: dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK037(ji)013:293: de nas gtor ma mgon bor gsal ba spyi bor bzhag la /
NK037(ji)013:294: slob dpon gyis bka' bsgos pa'i tshe phrin las thams cad thogs med du sgrub par bsam la /
NK037(ji)013:296: lha chen khyod dang mi 'bral ba'i //
NK037(ji)013:297: bka' dang dam la btags pa dang //
NK037(ji)013:298: phrin las rnam bzhi sgrub pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)013:299: dam rdzas gtor ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK037(ji)013:301: ma h+aa ba ling+ta a b+hika shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK037(ji)013:303: brgyud pa'i bshar 'debs dang dam bsgrag sngon du 'gro bas bka' bsgo rgyas bsdus ci rigs par bya /
NK037(ji)013:304: gtor ma las cung zad blangs pa bdud rtsi la
NK037(ji)013:305: sbyar ba dam bsre ba'i sngags kyis dam bzhag ltar
NK037(ji)013:308: gtor ma la yang bran te thun mong min pa'i dbang du'o //
NK037(ji)013:309: rjes dam tshig sgrol gzung dang man+dala yon 'bul rnams spyi dang 'dra zhing /
NK037(ji)013:310: rjes gtor 'bul gtang rag gi mchod bstod sogs rjes chog rnams gong bzhin bya'o //
NK037(ji)013:311: rnam 'gyur sna tshogs drag po'i gar //
NK037(ji)013:312: gnyis med ye shes rdo rje'i dngos //
NK037(ji)013:313: stag zhon sgrub thabs gnubs chen gyi //
NK037(ji)013:314: gdams pa'i rgya mtsho bcud du dril //
NK037(ji)013:315: stag zhon gnubs lugs kyi sgrub thabs dbang dang bcas
NK037(ji)013:316: pa'i le'u tshan gter chen 'gyur med rdo rje'i gsung
